{"tid":1544324,"cid":35,"subCid":0,"title":"Sun Mobile 10GB Plan 越用越差，而加日服都上唔到","createTime":"2019-09-05T13:50:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-16T09:19:26.000Z","uid":56178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"a9c48b02796785e1a1e7b25b32c0d291d1478048","tid":1544324,"uid":56178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":11,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T13:50:12.000Z","msg":"早上都好地地，過左黃昏之後喺觀塘搭緊巴士喺敢上唔到日服，正一垃圾。仲要啱啱續左約先黎搞啲敢既野，真心6uo<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"364b95e021718e5975e0f89f57d18b2127a4c14e","tid":1544324,"uid":52566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T13:51:01.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">香港人 應承我！<br />\n一日未答應五大訴求 都要繼續上街</span></strong></span><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月7日 (六) 1PM<br />\n機場交通壓力測試 (重考)</strong></div><br />\n<br />\n香港市民：<br />\n✅ 以遊客身份入機場觀賞飛機升降 <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n✅ 唔識路就坐多幾轉車 <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n✅ 必需繳付車資乘坐黨鐵<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n其他國藉居民：<br />\n各有各做, 自由發揮 <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nyixFQQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnyixFQQ.png&h=cc1f24a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月8日 (日) 2PM<br />\n香港人權與民主法案集會<br />\n美國駐港澳總領事館</strong></div><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2GKH20p.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2GKH20p.png&h=6178433f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a60dae5952377763129a5467ea0bcc059f82127b","tid":1544324,"uid":188376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T13:52:23.000Z","msg